hadiths[121]{hadithnumber,text}:
1250,ummul-momenin Sayeda Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs eik din mein baara rakatein bataur nafl Namaz padhta hai uskey liye unke badley jannat main eik ghar bana diya jata hai.''
1251,"Abdullah bin Shaqiq kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke nawaafil ke mutalliq maloom kiya to unhoney kaha : ''aap Zohar se pehley merey ghar mein chaar rakaten padhtey they. phir tashrif ley jatey aur logon ko Namaz padhatey . phir merey ghar mein laut aatey aur do rakaten padhtey. aur aap logon ko maghrib ki Namaz padhatey , phir merey ghar mein laut aatey aur do rakaten padhtey . aur aap unhen Isha ki Namaz padhatey , phir merey ghar mein tashrif latey aur do rakatein padhtey aur aap raat mein no rak'aat padhtey un mein witr (bhi) hota . aap eik lambi raat khadey ho kar Namaz padhtey aur eik lambi raat baith kar Namaz padhtey . jab aap khadey ho kar qirat kartey to rukoo bhi khadey ho kar kartey aur sajda kartey aur jab aap baith kar qirat kartey to rukoo bhi baith kar hi kartey aur sajda kartey. aur jab Fajr tulu ho jati to do rakaten padhtey , phir aap (masjid) tashrif ley jatey aur logon ko Fajr ki Namaz padhatey."
1252,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zohar se pehley do rakaten aur us (zohar) ke baad do rakaten , maghrib ke baad do rakaten apney ghar mein aur Namaze-Isha ke baad do rakaten padha kartey they. aur Jume ke baad nahin padhtey they yahan tak ke laut aatey aur do rakaten padhtey."
1253,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Zohar se pehley chaar rakaten aur namaze-Fajr se pehley ki do rakaten na chhoda kartey they.
1254,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kisi nawaafil par itni pabandi na farmatey they jitni ke Fajr ki sunnaton ki kartey they.
1255,Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fajr se pehley ki sunnaten is qadr halki padhtey they ke main kehti bhala aapney in mein Fatiha bhi padhi hai?
1256,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fajr ki sunnaton mein) قل ya أيها الكافرون (aur ( قل هو الله أحد ( ki qirat farmaee.
1257,"Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul (naqal ki gaee) hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko namaze-Fajr ki) jamaat ka waqt ho janey ki) ittilaa deney ke liye aaye to Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne usko kisi baat mein mashghool kar liya , yahan tak ke subh khoob safed ho gaee . phir Bilal khadey huey aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khabar di aur kaee baar khabar di , magar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif na laye, bil-aakhir jab nikley to logon ko Namaz padhaai . to Bilal ne aap se kaha ke Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne usko baaton mein laga liya tha aur wo us se kuch poochh rahi thin , yahan tak ke khoob subah ho gaee aur aapney bhi tashrif laney mein takheer kar di. aapney farmaya : ''main Fajr ki rakaten padh raha tha.'' kaha aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney bahut subh kar di. aapney farmaya : ''agar main is se bhi ziyada subh karta to main in sunnaton ko padhta aur umdagi aur khoobsurti se padhta.''"
1258,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Fajr ki do sunnaten mat chhodo agar-che dushman ke ghodey tum ko khaded rahey hon.''
1259,Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fajr ki sunnaton mein aksar ye aayaat tilawat kiya kartey they : ( { آمَنَّا بِاللَّهِ وَمَا أُنْزِلَ إِلَيْنَا } ( pehli rakaat mein . aur dusri rakaat mein ( { آمَنَّا بِاللَّهِ وَاشْهَدْ بِأَنَّا مُسْلِمُونَ } .
1260,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko Fajr ki sunnaton mein ye aayaat qirat kartey huey suna .pehli rakaat mein : ( { قُلْ آمَنَّا بِاللَّهِ وَمَا أُنْزِلَ عَلَيْنَا } ) aur dusri rakaat mein :( { رَبَّنَا آمَنَّا بِمَا أَنْزَلْتَ وَاتَّبَعْنَا الرَّسُولَ فَاكْتُبْنَا مَعَ الشَّاهِدِينَ } (ya ( { إِنَّا أَرْسَلْنَاكَ بِالْحَقِّ بَشِيرًا وَنَذِيرًا وَلَا تُسْأَلُ عَنْ أَصْحَابِ الْجَحِيمِ } ) ye shak Abdul-Azeez bin Muhammad Daraawardi ko hua hai.
1261,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi Fajr se pehley sunnaten padhey , to chahiye ke apni daain karwat par let jaey. ''Marwan bin Hakam ne un se kaha : kya bhala letnaa hi zaroori hai, kya masjid ki taraf chalna kafi nahin? ( Ubaidullah ki riwayat mein hai) kaha : nahin. ye baat Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko pahunchi to unhoney kaha : Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni jaan par bahut bojh dal diya hai. kahin (ghalti aur khata ke murtakib (mujrim) na ho jaeyn aur log bhi aetiraz kartey hain.). Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se kaha gaya : kya aap uska inkar kartey hain jo unhoney bayan kiya hai? unhoney kaha : nahin, lekin Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) jur'at mand hain aur ham khaaif (buzdil) ye baat Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ko pahunchi to unhoney kaha : is mein mera kya qusur hai ke maine yaad rakha hai aur ye bhool gaey hain."
1262,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aakhir raat mein jab apni Namaz mukammal farma letey to dekhtey , agar main jaag rahi hoti to mujh se baaten kerney lagtey aur agar soi hoti to jagaa detey aur do rakaten padhtey, phir let jatey , yahan tak ke aap ke paas muazzan aa kar aap ko Namaz subah ke waqt ki ittilaa deta , phir aap halki si do rakaten padhtey , phir Namaz ke liye nikal jatey."
1263,"Ummul-momenin Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Fajr ki do rakaten padh letey , to agar main soi hoti to let jatey aur agar jaag rahi hoti to mujh se baaten kerney lagtey."
1264,Hazrat Abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath namaze-Fajr ke liye nikla to aap jis kisi aadmi ke paas se guzartey usey Namaz ke liye aawaz detey ya apney paon se harkat detey. Ziyad ne ( حدثنا Abul-Fazal ki bajaey ( حدثنا Abul-Fuzail kaha hai.
1265,Hazrat Abdullah bin Sarjis (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik shakhs aaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fajr ki Namaz padha rahey they. usney do rakaat ( Fajr ki sunnaten ( padhein phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz mein shamil ho gaya. jab aap farigh huey to puchha : ''aey falan ! tumhari Namaz kaun si hai? wo jo tum ne akeley padhi ya wo jo hamarey sath padhi?''
1266,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab Namaz ( jamaat ( khadi ho jaey to phir farz ke alawa koi Namaz nahin.''
1267,"Hazrat Qais bin Amr (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik shakhs ko dekha jo Fajr ki Namaz ke baad do rakatein padh raha tha. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''subah ki Namaz do rakaten hain.'' to us shakhs ne jawab diya ke maine pehli do sunnatin nahin padhi thin, jo ab padhi hain. tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh ho gaey."
1268,Haamid bin Yahya Balkhi ne kaha ke Sufiyan ne kaha : Ata bin abi Ribah ye hadees Saad bin Saeed se bayan kiya kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha ke Abde-Rabba aur Yahya . ... . abnaaye Saeed . ... ne ye hadees mursal riwayat ki ke unke dada Zaid ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath Namaz padhi aur ye qissa bayan kiya.
1269,"Sayeda Umme-Habiba (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki paak biwi ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Zohar se pehley aur uskey baad chaar-chaar rakaaton ki pabandi kerega, wo aag par haram kar diya jaeyga.'' Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha, is hadees ko Ala bin Haris aur Sulaiman bin Musa ne Mak'hool se apni sanad se iski misl (jaisi) riwayat kiya hai."
1270,"Hazrat Abu-Ayub (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain, aapney farmaya : ''zohar se pehley ki chaar rak'aat ke un mein salam na ho, unke liye aasman ke darwazey khol diye jatey hain. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Yahya bin Saeed Qataan se mujhey ye baat pahunchi hai, unhoney kaha ke agar main Ubeda se kuch bayan karta to ye hadees riwayat karta. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Ubeda zaeef hai. aur ibne Minjaab ka naam Saham hai."
1271,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala us shakhs par rehem farmaai jo Asr se pehley chaar rakaten padhey.''
1272,Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Asr se pehley do rakaten padha kartey they.
1273,"Janab Kuraib maula ibne-Abbas se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas , Abdur-Rehman bin Azhar aur Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ne mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zauja (biwi) mohtarma Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein bheja aur kaha ke unhen ham sab ki taraf se salam kehna aur un se Asr ke baad do rakaaton ka masla poochhnaa aur kehna ke hamein maloom hua hai ke aap ye rakaten padhti hain jabke hamein ye baat pahunchi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se mana farmaya hai. chunanche main (yani kuraib ( unki khidmat mein hazir hua aur wo sab baat pahunchaai jo unhoney mujh se kahi thi to Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke jao Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) se maloom karo. main un hazraat ke paas wapis aaya aur unka jawab bataya to unhoney mujhey Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein bhej diya, is baat ke sath jo unhoney mujhey Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke mutalliq kahi thi. Hazrat Umme-Salma (Raziallahu anha) ne jawab diya ke maine Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna tha ke aap un se (asr ke baad Namaz sey) mana farmatey they lekin maine aap ko padhtey huey paya. (eik din) aap Asr ki Namaz padha kar tashrif laye aur merey yahan ansaar ke qabeela bani haram ki kuch aurten baithi thin , aapney ye rakaten padhein to maine khaadima ko aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas bheja , maine us se kaha ke ja kar aap ke paas khadi ho jana aur kehna ke Umme-Salma poochhti hain ke aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine aap ko suna hai ke aap in se mana farmatey hain aur main aap ko dekhti hun ke aap inhen padh rahey hain? agar aap apney haath se ishara farma den to un se zara door ho jana. chunanche khaadima ne aisey hi kiya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney haath se ishara kiya to wo peechhey hatt gaee. jab aap farigh huey to farmaya : ''aey dukhtar bani Umayya ! to ne Asr ke baad ki in do rakaaton ke mutalliq puchha hai to baat ye hai ke merey paas qabeela Abdul-Qais ke kuch log apni qaum ka Islam lekar aaye aur unhoney mujhey Zohar ke baad ki rakaaton se mashghool kar diya. to ye wohi do rakaten hain."
1274,Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Asr ke baad Namaz se mana farmaya hai siwaey iske ke Suraj ooncha ho.
1275,"Saiyedna Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fajr aur Asr ke alawa her farz Namaz ke baad do rakaat padha kartey they."
1276,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain, mujhey kaee pasandida logon ne bataya , un mein Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) bhi hain balke un sab mein Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sab se badh kar pasandida hain, unhoney bataya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''subh ki Namaz ke baad koi Namaz nahin yahan tak ke Suraj tulu ho jaey. aur namaze-Asr ke baad koi Namaz nahin yahan tak ke Suraj ghuroob ho jaey.''"
1277,"Hazrat Amr bin Abasa Sulmi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! raat ka kaun sa hissey ziyada maqbool hota hai? aapney farmaya : '' aakhir raat ka darmiyani hissey . so jis qadr ji chahey Namaz padho . be-shak Namaz mein farishtey hazir hotey hain aur uska ajr likha jata hai yahan tak ke Fajr padh lo . phir ruk jao yahan tak ke Suraj nikal aaye aur eik ya do nezon ke barabar ooncha aa jaey. be-shak ye shaitan ke do seengon ke darmiyan tulu hota hai aur us waqt kuffar uski ibadat kartey hain. phir Namaz padhtey raho , be-shak Namaz mein farishtey hazir hotey aur uska ajr likha jata hai yahan tak ke neze ka saya us ( neze (ke barabar ho jaey (yani do-pehar ho jaey aur koi zayed saya baqi na rahey) to ruk jao . be-shak (us waqt ( jahannam bhadkai jati hai aur uskey darwazey khol diye jatey hain. jab Suraj dhal jaey to jis qadr ji chahey Namaz padho , be-shak Namaz mein farishtey hazir hotey hain, yahan tak ke Asr padh lo , phir ruk jao yahan tak ke Suraj ghuroob ho jaey. be-shak ye shaitan ke do seengon ke beech ghuroob hota hai aur (us waqt ( kuffar uski ibadat kartey hain.'' aur lambi hadees bayan ki . Abbas bin Salim ne kaha ke Abu-Salaam ne mujhey Abu-Umama se aisey hi bayan kiya hai siwaey iske ke mujh se koi naa-daanista (bagair jaane bujhe) bhool ho gaee ho to Allah se istighfar aur tauba karta hun."
1278,Janab Yasar maula ibne-Umar kehtey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne mujhey dekha ke main tulu Fajr ke baad Namaz padh raha tha to unhoney farmaya : aey Yasar ! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur ham ye Namaz padha kartey they to aapney farmaya : '' tumhara hazir (mojud) shakhs apney ghayeb ko bata dey ke siwaye do rakaaton ke tulu Fajr ke baad Namaz na padha karo.''
1279,Aswad aur Masruq (dono) ne kaha : ham Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ki baabat gawahi detey hain ke unhoney bayan kiya ke koi din aisa na guzarta tha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Asr ke baad do rakatein na padhtey hon. (yani her roz bila-nagha padha kartey they.)
1280,Janab Zakwaan maula Aaysha se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne un se bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Asr ke baad Namaz padha kartey they jabke logon ko us se mana kartey they. khud wisaal kartey (yani do do din ke ikatthey rozey rakhtey ya us se ziyada ke bhi aur darmiyan mein iftaar na kartey) aur logon ko wisaal se mana farmatey they.
1281,"Hazrat Abdullah Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Namaze-Maghrib se pehley do rakaten padha karo.'' phir farmaya : ''Namaze-Maghrib se pehley do rakaten padha karo, jo chahey.'' ye is dar se ke kahin log isey sunnat na bana len."
1282,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein maghrib se pehley do rakaten padhi hain. ( Mukhtaar kehtey hain ( maine Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : kya aap ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dekha tha? unhoney kaha : haan ! aapney ham ko hukm diya, na mana farmaya."
1283,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Mughaffal (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''har do azaanon ke darmiyan Namaz hai. har do azaanon ke darmiyan Namaz hai, jo chahey.''"
1284,"Janab Taaus kehtey hain ke Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se maghrib se pehley ki do rakaaton ke mutalliq puchha gaya to unhoney kaha : maine kisi ko nahin dekha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein usey padhta ho. aur Asr ke baad do rakaaton ki rukhsat di. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke maine Yahya bin Maeen ko suna, kehtey they ke raawi hadees Abu-Shuaib darasal Shuaib hai, Shoba ko uskey naam mein weham hua hai."
1285,Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''subah hoti hai to ibne-Adam ke ang-ang par sadqa lazim ho chuka hota hai. chunanche uska apney milney walon ko salam kehna sadqa hai. neki ka hukm dena sadqa hai. burai se rokna sadqa hai. raastey se aziyat wali chiz door karna sadqa hai. aur ehliya se ham bistar hona sadqa hai. aur un sab se chaasht ki do rakaten kifaayat karti hain. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Ibaad ki riwayat ziyada kamil hai. aur Musaddad ne apni riwayat mein Amr aur nahi ka bayan nahin kiya balke kaha : ye aur ye . aur ibne-Mani' ne apni riwayat mein izafa kiya : Sahaba ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! insan apni nafsani khahish puri karey aur ye uskey liye sadqa baney? (kyon kar?) aapney farmaya : ''batao agar wo ye kaam halal jagah mein na karta (yani zina karta) to kya gunah na hota?''
1286,"Janab Abul-Aswad Wali kehtey hain ke ham Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas they ke unhoney kaha : ''subah hoti hai to tumharey eik-eik ke ang-ang par sadqa lazim ho chuka hota hai aur her roz aisey hota hai. chunanche uski har Namaz , roza , hajj , tasbih , takbir aur tahmeed sadqa hoti hai.'' Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ye aamaale-saalah shumar farmaai , phir farmaya : '' tumhen in sab se chaasht ki do rakaten kifaayat karti hain.''"
1287,"Janab Sehal bin Muaz bin Anas Juhni apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs Fajr ki Namaz se farigh ho kar apni jaey Namaz par baitha rahey aur zuhaa ( chaasht ( ki do rakatein padh kar uthey aur us dauran mein khair hi ki baat karey to uski khataeyn maaf kar di jati hain, chahe samandar ki jhaag se ziyada hon.''"
1288,"Hazrat Abu-Umama (Raziallahu anhu) riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik Namaz ke baad dusri Namaz , is tarah ke unke beech koi  fuzul aur bekar baat na ho, (is amal sey) illiyeen mein naam darj ho jata hai.''"
1289,"Hazrat Nuaim bin Hammaar (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, farmatey they : ''Shan wala Allah farmata hai : aey ibne-Adam ! to merey liye shuru din mein chaar rak'aat padhney se aajiz na reh , main aakhir din tak teri kifaayat karunga.''"
1290,Hazrat Umme-Haani binte-Abi Talib (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fateh Makka ke roz chaasht ki aath rak'aat padhi thin . aap her do rakaat par salam phertey they. Ahmed bin Saleh ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fateh Makka ke din chaasht ki Namaz padhi aur usi ke misl (jaisi) zikr kiya. ibne-Sarah ne kaha : Umme- Haani (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey yahan tashrif laye . ... . aur Namaze-chaasht ka naam nahin liya. (balke waisay hi kaha ke aapney aath rak'aat padhin) sabiqa hadees ke maani mein .
1291,"Janab ibne-Abi Laila kehtey hain ke hamein Umme-Haani (Raziallahu anha) ke alawa kisi ne khabar nahin di ke isney dekha ho ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Namaz chaasht padhi, Umme-Haani (Raziallahu anha) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Fateh Makka ke roz uskey ghar mein ghusl kiya aur aath rakatein padhein (uskey siwa) aur kisi ne nahin dekha ke iskey baad aapney ye rak'aat padhi hon."
1292,"Janab Abdullah bin Shaqiq kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chaasht ki Namaz padha kartey they? kaha nahin, siwaey iske ke safar se tashrif latey . maine puchha : kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) suraten mila kar padh liya kartey they? unhoney kaha : haan . mufassal mein se (yani aakhiri manzil ki soorton mein sey) ."
1293,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) zauja Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne zuhaa ke nafl kabhi nahin padhey , main albatta padhti hun. bila-shuba Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kuch amal karna chahtey magar chhod detey they, ke log amal karengey to kahen un par farz na kar diya jaey."
1294,Janab Samaak kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Jabir bin Samura (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke kya aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki majlis mein baitha kartey they? unhoney kaha : haan bahut ziyada . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jahan Fajr ki Namaz ada farmatey wahan se us waqt tak na uthtey jab tak ke Suraj tulu na ho jata . jab ( Suraj ( tulu ho jata to phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khadey ho jatey.
1295,Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' raat aur din ki Namaz do do rakaat hai.''
1296,"Janab Abdullah bin Haris, Muttalib se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kartey hain ke aapney farmaya : ''Namaz do-do rakaat hai. yun ke tum her do rakaat par tashahud padho , apni zaari (bebasi) aur miskini ka izhar karo, dono haath uthao aur kaho ( اللهم ! اللهم ! ( ''aey Allah ! aey Allah ! '' aur jo yun na karey to uski ye Namaz naqis hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) se raat ki Namaz do rakaat honey ke mutalliq puchha gaya to kaha : chaho to do do rakaat padh lo aur chaho to chaar-chaar."
1297,"Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : aey Abbas ! aey chacha jaan ! kya main aap ko eik hadiya na dun? Atiya aur tohfa na dun? kya main aap ko das baaten na sikha dun. jab aap un par amal karengey tu Allah aap ke agley pichhley, puirani naye ( khata ( , umda , chhotey badey , poshida aur zahir sab hi gunah maaf farma dega. das baaten ye hain ke aap chaar rak'aat padhen. her rakaat mein aap sura Fatiha aur eik surat padhen. jab aap pehli rakaat mein qirat se farigh ho jaeyn aur qiyam mein hon to pandarah baar ye tasbih padhein : (سبحان الله والحمدلله wla إله إلا الله والله أكبر)phir rukoo keren aur haalate rukoo mein das baar yehi tasbih padhen. phir rukoo se sar uthaeyn aur das baar yehi tasbih padhen. phir sajda keren aur sajdey mein das baar ye padhen. phir sajdey se sar uthaeyn to yehi tasbih das baar padhen. phir doosra sajda keren to us mein bhi das baar padhein. phir sar uthaeyn to das baar padhein. her rakaat mein ye kul pachhattar (75) tasbeehaat huin . aur aap chaaron rakaaton mein aisey hi karen. agar himmat ho to her roz (ye Namaz) padha karen. agar her roz na padh saken to her haftey main eik baar , agar haftey mein na padh saken to eik mahiney main eik baar padhen . agar ye na kar saken to saal main eik baar padhen. agar saal mein bhi na padh saken to apni zindagi main eik baar padh len.''"
1298,"Janab Abul Jauza kehtey hain ke mujh se eik sahabi ne bayan kiya jinhen log Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) samajhtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : ''kal merey paas aana main tumhen eik hadiya dunga , Atiya dun ga. ''mujhey khayal hua ke aap mujhey koi maal inayat farmaeyn gey .) mein hazir hua to ( aapney farmaya : ''jab Suraj dhal jaey to khadey ho jao aur chaar rakaten padho. ''aur mazkura baala ki manind zikr kiya. is riwayat mein kaha : ''jab tum doosrey sajdey se sar uthao to theek tarah se baith jao aur das baar (سبحان الله), das baar (الحمد الله), das baar ( الله اكبر (aur das baar (لا إله إلا الله) padho . jab tak ye na padh lo khadey na ho. aur phir chaaron rakaaton mein aisey hi karo.'' farmaya : ''agar tum ehle zameen mein sab se ziyada gunah gaar bhi huey to us se wo sab maaf kar diye jaeyngey.'' maine kaha : agar main is waqt mein na padh sakoon to? aapney farmaya : ''raat din mein kisi bhi waqt padh lo. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Hibbaan bin Hilal, Hilal (Al raazi)  ke mamu hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain is riwayat ko Mustamir bin Rayyan ne Abul Jauza se unhoney Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se Mauqufan bayan kiya hai. aur isey Rooh bin Musaiyab aur Jaafar bin Sulaiman ne Amr bin Malik nakari se unhoney Abul Jauza se unhoney ibne-Abbas se unka qaul bayan kiya hai. Rooh ki riwayat mein hai ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne farmaya : ye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hadees hai. ( meri apni baat nahin hai.) yani mujhey hadeese-nabawi keh kar bayan ki gaee."
1299,Urwa bin Ruvaim Ansari se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Jaafar ko farmaya : baqiya hadees ke alfaz wohi hain jo ke Mehdi bin Memun ne naqal farmaai lekin is riwayat mein in alfaz ka izafa hai ke unhoney pehli rakaat ke doosrey sajdey ke baarey mein farmaya.
1300,Hazrat Kab bin Ajra se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) qabeela bani Abdul-Ash'hal ki masjid mein tashrif laye aur wahan maghrib ki Namaz padhi . Namaz ke baad aapney unko dekha ke wo uskey baad nafl padh rahey hain. aapney farmaya : ''ye gharon ki Namaz hai.''
1301,"Janab Saeed bin Jubair , Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se raawi hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) maghrib ke baad ki rakaaton mein qirat is qadr taweel kartey ke ehale-masjid (gharon ko) chaley jatey.  Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke Nasar ne Yaqoob se iskey jaisi musnad riwayat ki hai. isi ke sath Muhammad bin Isa bin Tubaa'a ne ba-waasta Nasar, Yaqoob se iskey jaisi riwayat ki hai."
1302,"Hazrat Saeed bin Jubair ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani mursal hadees bayan ki.  Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain : maine Muhammad bin Humaid se suna, unhoney kaha : maine Yaqoob se suna, wo kehtey they har wo riwayat jo main tumhen Jaafar se wo Saeed bin Jubair se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan karta hun wo sab ba-waasta ibne-Abbas , Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se musnad (wusul hui) hain."
1303,"Shuraih bin Haani Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey hain, Shuraih ne kaha ke maine un se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ke baarey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab bhi Isha ki Namaz padh kar merey yahan tashrif latey to chaar ya chhe rak'aat padhtey . eik raat barish ho gaee ham ne aap ke liye chamdaa bichha diya, isliye goya main dekh rahi hun ke uskey eik surakh se pani nikal raha tha. aur maine aap ko kabhi nahin dekha ke) Namaz ke beech mein) apney kapdon ko mitti se bachatey hon."
1304,Janab Ikrima raawi hain ke Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne sura muzammil ki tafseer mein farmaya ke :( { قُمِ اللَّيْلَ إِلَّا قَلِيلًا نِصْفَهُ } ) ko usi surat ki dusri aayat ( { عَلِمَ أَنْ لَنْ تُحْصُوهُ فَتَابَ عَلَيْكُمْ فَاقْرَءُ وامَا تَيَسَّرَ مِنَ الْقُرْآنِ } ) ne mansookh kar diya. aur ( نَاشِئَةُ اللَّيْلِ ) se raat ke ibtidaai (shuruati) hissey mein jaagna murad hai. aur Sahaba kiram ki Namaz (raat ki Namaz) raat ke ibtidaai (shuruati) hissey mein hua karti thi. aur us waqt mein Allah ka farz karda qiyamullail theek theek ada kerney mein ziyada aasani hai kyonkey so janey ke baad insan ko khabar nahin hoti ke Kab bedaar hoga (ya na bedaar ho sakega). ( وأقوم قيلا ) ka mafhoom ye hai ke Quran ko samajhney ke liye ye waqt bahut behtar hai aur ( { إِنَّ لَكَ فِي النَّهَارِ سَبْحًا طَوِيلًا } ) se murad lambi fursat hai. (yani din ke waqt duniyaawi umur (baton) mein mashghooliyat hoti hai is liye raat ka waqt ibadat mein lagaao.)
1305,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain : jab Sura Muzammil ka ibtidaai (shuruati) hissey ( قُمِ اللَّيْلَ إِلَّا قَلِيلًا . . . . .) nazil hua to Sahaba kiram aisey qiyam kartey they jaisey ke Ramazan mein qiyam kartey hain yahan tak ke is surat ka aakhiri hissey nazil hua . aur in dono hisson ke nuzool main eik saal ka farq tha.
1306,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi sota hai to shaitan uski guddhi ke paas teen girhen laga deta hai aur har gireh par ye dam karta hai. raat lambi hai soyaa reh agar wo jaag jaey, Allah ka zikr karey to eik gireh khul jati hai agar wo wuzu kar ley to dusri khul jati hai. aur agar Namaz padh ley to teesri bhi khul jati hai aur wo hashshaash bashshaash khush khush subah karta hai. warna buri haalat aur kasl mandi (susti) ki kaifiyat mein subh karta hai.''"
1307,Hazrat Abdullah bin Ubai Qais (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : ''raat ka qiyam mat chhodo kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey na chhodtey they. agar aap bimar hotey ya kasl mandi (susti) ki kaiyfiyat hoti to baith kar Namaz padh liya kartey they.''
1308,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Reham farmaai Allah taala us bandey par jo raat ko uth kar Namaz padhta aur apni biwi ko jagata hai. agar wo inkar karey to uskey munh par pani ke chheentey maarta hai. aur rehem farmaai Allah taala us bandi par jo raat ko uth kar Namaz padhti aur apney shohar ko jagaati hai. agar wo inkar karey to uskey munh par pani ke chheentey maarti hai.''
1309,Hazrat Abu-Saeed aur Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anha) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab shohar apni ehliya ko raat ke waqt jagata hai aur wo dono Namaz padhtey ya do rakaten padhtey hain to unka indraaj zaakireen aur zaakiraat mein ho jata hai.'' ibne Kaseer ne usko marfoo zikr nahin kiya aur na Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka naam hi liya balke isey Abu-Saeed ka kalam bataya. Imam Abu-Dawud farmatey hain ke ibne Mehdi ne Sufiyan se riwayat kiya aur kaha : mera khayal hai ke usney Abu-Huraira ka naam liya . Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Sufiyan ki hadees mauquf hai.
1310,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) zaujae Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se manqul hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se kisi ko Namaz mein ungh aaney lagey to usey chahiye ke so jaey, yahan tak ke uski neend puri ho jaey kyonkey jab koi oonghte huey Namaz padhey to ho sakta hai ke wo istighfar karna chahta ho magar apney aap ko gaaliyaan hi deney lagey.''"
1311,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi raat ko uth kar Namaz padhey aur phir Quran ko apni zaban par bhari mehsoos kerney lagey , usey maloom na ho ke kya keh raha hai to chahiye ke so jaey.''"
1312,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) masjid mein dakhil huey aur do sutonon ke darmiyan eik rassi latki hui thi. puchha : ''ye rassi kaisi hai? ''kaha gaya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ye Hamna binte-Jahash Namaz padhti hai, jab thak jati hai to uskey sath latak jati hai. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tak taqat ho Namaz padhey aur jab thak jaey to baith jaey.'' Ziyad ne riwayat kiya : '' aapney puchha ye kya hai? '' wo (Sahaba kiraam) kehney lagey : ye Zenab ki hai, Namaz padhti rehti hai, jab sust ho jati hai ya thak jati hai to isey thaam leti hai. aapney farmaya : ''isey khol do . tumhen chahiye ke jab tak chusti se Namaz padhi jaey padho , jab susti mehsoos karo ya thak jao to baith jao.''"
1313,"ibne-Wahab bin Abdul-Qaari se riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha : maine Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ko suna, bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apna rozana ka wazeefa na padh saka ho aur so gaya ho aur phir usey Fajr aur Zohar ke darmiyan padh ley to uskey liye aisey hi likha jata hai goya usney usko raat mein padha ho.''"
1314,Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki pak biwi ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs raat ko Namaz ada karta ho magar kisi raat us par neend ghalib aa jaey to uskey liye uski Namaz ka ajr likh diya jata hai aur neend uskey liye sadqa hoti hai.''
1315,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''hamara Shan wala Rab har raat jab raat ka aakhiri teesra hissey baqi hota hai aasmane duniya par tashrif lata hai aur farmata hai : kaun hai jo mujh se dua karey aur main qubul karun. kaun hai jo mujh se maangey aur main usey dun . aur kaun hai jo mujh se maafi chahey aur main usko bakhsh dun.''
1316,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke bila-shuba Shan wala Allah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko raat mein jagaa deta tha. chunanche sahar ( subah ( na ho paati thi ke aap apney mamool ki ibadat se farigh ho chukey hotey they.
1317,Masruq kehtey hain ke maine ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ke mutalliq puchha ke aap kis waqt Namaz padha kartey they? to unhoney kaha : aap jab murgh ki pukar suntey to uth khadey hotey aur Namaz padhtey they.
1318,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab bhi merey yahan hotey to sehri ke waqt soey huey hotey they.
1319,Hazrat Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab koi gham laahiq hota to Namaz padhney lagtey they.
1320,"Hazrat Rabeea bin Kab Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath raat guzaarta tha, aap ko wuzu ka pani aur deegar zarooriyaat pesh karta tha. ( eik baar ( aapney farmaya : ''maango . ... ! '' maine arz kiya : jannat mein aap ki rafaqat (dosti) (ka saail (sawali) hun) farmaya : ''koi dusri chiz?'' maine arz kiya : bas yehi hai. aapney farmaya : '' to to apney is matlab ke liye kasrate-sujood se meri madad kar.''"
1321,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) us aayate-kareema : ( { تَتَجَافَى جُنُوبُهُمْ عَنِ الْمَضَاجِعِ يَدْعُونَ رَبَّهُمْ خَوْفًا وَطَمَعًا وَمِمَّا رَزَقْنَهُمْ يُنْفِقُونَ } ) ''unke pehlu bistaron se door rehtey hain, wo apney rab ko khauf aur umeed se pukartey hain aur jo ham ne unko diya us mein se kharch kartey hain.'' ki tafseer mein farmatey hain ke ye log ( Sahaba ( maghrib aur Isha ke darmiyan jaagtey they, yani Namaz padhtey they. aur Janab Hasan Basri is se raat ka qiyam ( tahajjud ( murad letey hain."
1322,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aayate-kareema : ( {كَانُوا قَلِيلًا مِنَ اللَّيْلِ مَا يَهْجَعُونَ} ) ''ye log raat mein bahut kam sotey they.'' ki tafseer mein farmaya ke Sahaba kiram maghrib aur Isha ke beech Namaz padha kartey they. aur Yahya ki riwayat mein ye izafa hai ke aayate kareema ( { تَتَجَافَى جُنُوبُهُمْ } ) se bhi yehi murad hai.
1323,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jab tum mein se koi raat ko uthey to chahiye ke) pehley ( do halki rakatein padhey.''
1324,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ''jab . ... .'' aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya aur is mein mazeed kaha : ''phir uskey baad jis qadr chahey lambi Namaz padhey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke is hadees ko Hammad bin Salma , Zuhair bin Muawiya aur eik jamaat ne Hisham bin Muhammad se riwayat kiya hai, to unhoney usko Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) par mauquf kiya hai. aur isi tarah is ( hadees ( ko Ayub aur ibne Aun ne riwayat kiya hai, to unhoney bhi usko Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) par mauquf kiya hai. aur ibn Aun , Muhammad bin Sirin se riwayat kartey hain, to us mein hai ke un dono ( pehli rak'aat ( ko mukhtasar rakhey ."
1325,Hazrat Abdullah bin Habshi Khasami (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se puchha gaya : kaun sa amal afzal hai? aapney farmaya : ''(Namaz mein) lamba qiyam.''
1326,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik shakhs ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se raat ki Namaz ke baarey mein puchha , to aapney farmaya : ''raat ki Namaz do do rakaat hai. jab tum mein se kisi ko subah ho janey ka andesha ho to eik rakat padh ley . ye uski padhi hui Namaz ko witr bana dey gi.''"
1327,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke) raat ki Namaz mein) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki qirat is qadr ( buland ( hoti thi ke sehan mein baitha aadmi sun sakta tha jabke aap ghar mein (yani kamrey mein) hotey they.
1328,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko kabhi buland aawaz se aur kabhi dheemi aawaz se qirat kartey they. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke Abu-Khalid Waalbi ka naam Hurmuz hai.
1329,"Hazrat Abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke eik raat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) nikley aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se guzrey , wo Namaz padh rahey they aur unki aawaz dheemi thi. aur Umar-bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas se guzrey , wo bhi Namaz padh rahey they, unki aawaz buland thi. jab wo dono Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas ikhattey huey to aapney farmaya : ''aey Abu-Bakar ! main tumharey paas se guzra, tum Namaz padh rahey they aur tumhari aawaz dheemi thi ?'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine jis se munajat ki usey sunaya . phir aapney umr se kaha : ''main tumharey paas se guzra, tum buland aawaz se Namaz padh rahey they?'' unhoney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main sotay ko jagaa raha tha aur shaitan ko bhagaa raha tha. Hasan ne apni riwayat mein izafa kiya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Abu-Bakar ! apni aawaz kuchh buland kiya karo.'' aur umr se farmaya : ''tum apni aawaz kuchh dheemi rakha karo.''"
1330,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yehi qissa bayan kartey hain magar is hadees mein ye nahin hai ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : ''apni aawaz qadrey oonchi karo.'' aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : ''apni aawaz kuch dheemi rakho.'' is riwayat mein mazeed ye hai ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''maine suna tum kuch is surat se aur kuch is surat se padh rahey they.'' unhoney kaha : ye eik umda kalam hai. Allah ne uskey baaz ko baaz ke sath jama farma diya hai to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum sab ne durust kiya.''
1331,Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik shakhs raat ko utha aur qirat karney laga aur apni aawaz buland rakhi . jab subah hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah falan par rehem farmaai ! usney aaj raat mujhey kitni hi aayaten yaad dila di jin mein mujhey zahul ho raha tha. Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke isko Harun Nahwi ne Hammad bin Salma se bayan kiya to Sura Aale-Imran ki aayat :( { وَكَأَيٍّ مِنْ نَبِيٍّ } ( naqal ki .
1332,Hazrat Abu-Saeed ( Khudri ( (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne masjid mein aetikaf farmaya. aapney logon ko suna ke wo oonchi aawaz se qirat kar rahey hain. aapney parda hataayaa aur farmaya : ''khabrdar ! tum bila-shuba sab ke sab apney rab se munajat kar rahey ho magar koi doosrey ko hergiz eza (takleef) na dey aur qirat main apni aawaz doosrey par buland na karey.'' ya farmaya : ''Namaz mein (apni aawaz buland na karey.'')
1333,Hazrat Aqba-bin-Aamir-juhni (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Quran ko oonchi aawaz se padhney wala aisey hai jaisey koi dikha kar sadqa karey. aur dheemi aawaz se Quran padhney wala aisey hai jaisey koi makhfi (chhipe) taur par sadqa dey.''
1334,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) farmati hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat mein das rakaten padha kartey , aur eik rakat witr padhtey . aur) baad Azan ( do rakaten Fajr ki padhtey. is tarah ye kal tehra rak'aat huin."
1335,Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) zaujae (biwi)-nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko giyara rak'aat padha kartey they. in mein se eik rakat witr hoti . in se farigh honey ke baad aap apni daain karwat par let jatey they.
1336,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Namaze Isha se farigh honey ke baad se Fajr tulu honey ke darmiyan mein giyara rakatein padha kartey they. her do rakaaton par salam kehtey aur eik rakat witr padhtey. aap apney sajdey mein itni der rehtey ke jis mein tum pachas aayaten padh lo. aur muazzan jab Fajr ki Azan kehta , aap uth kar halki halki do rakaten padhtey , phir apni daain karwat par let jatey yahan tak ke muazzan aa jata."
1337,"ibne-Shahab ne apni sabiqa sanad sey, aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya. is mein hai : aap eik rakat witr padhtey aur sajdey mein itni der rehtey ke tum mein se eik shakhs pachas aayaten padh ley . aur muazzan jab Azan Fajr se farigh hota aur Fajr wazeh taur par tulu ho chuki hoti . aur mazkura hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya, albatta riwayten eik doosrey se kuch izaafey se bayan kartey hain."
1338,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat mein tehra rakaat padhtey , in mein se paanch rakaat witr hoten . aap in paanchon rak'aat mein kisi mein bhi (tashahud) mein na baithtey . balke aakhir hi mein baithtey aur salam phertey . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke is riwayat ko ibne-Numair ne Hisham se mazkura baala hadees ki manind bayan kiya hai."
1339,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se manqul (naqal ki gaee) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko tehra rak'aat padha kartey , phir jab subah ki Azan suntey to halki si do rakaten padhtey."
1340,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko tehra rak'aat padha kartey. aap ( pehley ( aath rak'aat padhtey , phir eik rakat witr padhtey . uskey baad baith kar do rakatein padhtey . jab aap ka irada hota ke rukoo keren to khadey ho kar rukoo kartey. phir Azan Fajr aur iqaamat ke beech do rakaten padhtey."
1341,"Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman ne Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha ke Ramazan mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz kaisey hoti thi ? to unhoney kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Ramazan ya ghair Ramazan mein giyara rak'aat se ziyada nahin padha kartey they. aap chaar rakaten padhtey , mat poochho ke wo kitni umda aur kitni taweel hoti thin ! phir chaar rakaten padhtey , mat poochho ke wo kitni umda aur kitni taweel hoti thin ! (yani intehai thehrao aur itminan se padhtey aur qirat had se zyada taweel hoti thi. ( phir teen rak'aat padhtey . Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain ke maine aap se puchha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya aap witron  se pehley so jatey hain? aapney farmaya : ''aey Aaisha ! meri aankhen soti hain, magar dil nahin sota.''"
1342,"Saad bin Hisham kehtey hain ke maine apni biwi ko Talaq de-di aur Madiney chala aaya taake yahan ki apni jaaidaad farokht karkey aslaha waghaira kharid lun aur jihad ke liye nikal jaun . chunanche main baaz Sahaba kiram se mila to unhoney bataya ke ham mein se chhe aadmiyon ne aisey hi karna chaha tha, magar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko mana farma diya tha. aur farmaya : ''tumharey liye Allah ke Rasool mein behtareen namoona hai.'' chunanche main Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke paas aaya . maine un se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke witron ke mutalliq puchha to unhoney kaha : main tumhen wo shakhsiyat batata hun jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke witron ke mutalliq sab se ziyada ba-khabar hai. Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas chaley jao . main Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan aaya aur Hakim bin Aflah ko apney sath chalney ko kaha, unhoney inkar kiya. maine unko qasam di to wo merey sath chal padey . ham ne Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se mulaqat ki ijazat chahi to unhoney puchha : kaun ho? kaha : Hakim bin Aflah. puchha : tumharey sath aur kaun hai? kaha : Saad bin Hisham . kehney lagin : wohi Hisham bin Aamir jo ahad ke roz qatl ho gaey they? maine kaha : haan . wo kehney lagin : Aamir bahut bhaley insan they. maine kaha : aey Ummul-momenin ! mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke khulq ( akhlaq aur aadaat (ke mutalliq irshad farmaen. kehney lagin : kya tum Quran nahin padhtey ho? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka khulq bas Quran hi tha. maine kaha : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qiyamul-lail ke mutalliq irshad farmaen . kehney lagein : kya tum Sura-Muzammil (يأيها المزمل ( nahin padhtey ho? maine kaha : kyon nahin. unhoney kaha : is surat ka ibtidaai (shuruati) hissey nazil hua to as-haabe-Rasul (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne qiyam karna shuru kiya, yahan tak ke unke paon sooj jatey. aur is surat ka aakhiri hissey baara mahiney aasman par rokey rakha gaya. (yani nazil nahin hua .) phir kahin uska aakhiri hissey nazil hua to raat ka qiyam nafl qarar paya jabkey pehley farz tha. maine kaha : mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke witr ke mutalliq bayan farmaen . wo kehney lagin : aap aath rak'aat padhtey , un mein aap sirf aathwin rakaat par tashahud ke liye baithtey , phir uthtey aur eik aur rakaat padhtey . aap aathwin aur naween rakaat hi par baithtey aur naween par salam phertey . uskey baad aap do rakaten padhtey , baithey huey. bete ! ye giyara huin. phir jab aap badi umr ke ho gaey aur kuch farba bhi , to saat rak'aat witr padhney lagey . aap chhatti aur saatwin rakaat par baithtey aur saatwin hi par salam phertey . phir do rakaten padhtey jabkey aap baithey huey hotey . bete ! ye is tarah no rak'aat hotin. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kabhi bhi sari raat subh tak qiyam nahin farmaya. aur aapney kabhi bhi eik raat mein Quran khatam nahin kiya. aur Ramazan ke alawa kisi bhi mahiney ke purey rozey nahin rakhey. aur jab koi Namaz (yani nafl ( shuru kar letey to us par hameshgi farmatey. agar kabhi kisi raat neend ka ghalba ho jata to din mein baara rak'aat padhtey. (Saad kehtey hain) phir main Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke paas aaya aur unhen ye sab bataya to unhoney kaha : qasam Allah ki ! yehi hadees hai (jo mein chahta tha.) agar main un se boltaa hota to main khud unki khidmat mein hazir hota aur bil-mushaafa sunta . Saad ne kaha : agar mujhey maloom hota ke aap un se nahin boltey hain to main aap ko ye hadees na sunata."
1343,"Saeed ne Qatada se apni sanad se usi mazkura hadees ki manind riwayat kiya. kaha : aap aath rak'aat padhtey , un mein kisi mein bhi na baithtey , sirf aathwin rakaat par baithtey , Allah ka zikr aur dua kartey phir salam phertey is tarah ke hamein sunwaate (yani buland aawaz se salam kehtey) phir salam ke baad baithey-baithey do rakaten padhtey, phir eik rakat padhtey. bete ! ye kul giyara rakaten hotin. phir jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) badi umr ke ho gaey aur kuch farba bhi to aap saat rakaat witr padhney lagey aur salam ke baad baithey-baithey do rakaten padhtey. sabiqa hadees ke ham-maani ''bil-mushaafa sunta'' tak bayan kiya."
1344,Saeed ne yehi hadees bayan ki . unhoney kaha : salam kehtey is tarah ke hamein sunwaate . jaisey ke Yahya bin Saeed ne riwayat kiya.
1345,"Muhammad bin Bashaar ne ibne-Abi Adi sey, unhoney Saeed se yehi hadees riwayat ki . ibne Bashaar ne Yahya bin Saeed ki hadees ki manind bayan kiya, magar kaha : aap salam kehtey eik salam aur hamein sunwaate."
1346,"Bahaz bin Hakeem ne kaha ke Zarara bin Ufee bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki raat ki Namaz ke mutalliq puchha gaya to unhoney kaha : aap Isha ki jamaat ke baad ghar laut'tey to chaar rakaat ( sunnate-Isha ( padhtey . phir apney bistar par aa jatey aur so jatey. aur aap ke wuzu ka pani aap ke sarhaaney dhanp kar rakha hota, miswak bhi rakhi hoti yahan tak ke Allah aap ko raat mein aap ke muqarrara waqt par utha deta. phir aap ( jaagtey ( miswak aur kamil wuzu kartey aur apney musalley par tashrif ley aatey. aap aath rak'aat padhtey , un mein aap Ummul-Quran (Sura Fatiha (aur Quran ki koi surat padhtey aur jo Allah chahta . aap un rak'aat mein (koi tashahud) na baithtey , sirf aathwin rakaat mein baithtey magar salam na phertey , phir naween mein qirat kartey , phir baithtey aur dua kartey jo Allah chahta . un duaon mein Allah se sawal kartey aur usi ki taraf ruju aur raghbat (dilchaspi) ka izhar farmatey, phir salam kehtey eik hi salam badi oonchi aawaz sey, is qadr oonchi aawaz ke qarib hota ke ghar waley jaag jaeyn , phir ( baithey baithey do rakaten padhtey) sura Fatiha padhtey aur rukoo kartey baithey hue, phir dusri rakaat padhtey aur rukoo aur sajda kartey baithey hue, phir khoob dua kartey jo Allah chahta , phir salam phertey aur uth jatey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz isi andaz se rahi , magar jab aap farba ho gaey to aapney no rakaaton mein se do rakaten kam kar lin , yani witr ke baghair chhe rak'aat aur witr ke sath saat rak'aat padhney lagey aur unke baad do rakaten padhtey jabkey aap baithey huey hotey , yahan tak ke usi aadat par aap ki rooh qabz hui."
1347,"Bahaz bin Hakeem ne apni sabiqa sanad se ye hadees bayan ki aur kaha . ... aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Isha ki Namaz padh kar apney bistar par aa jatey. usney chaar rakaat padhney ka zikr nahin kiya. ... aur bayan kiya ke aap aath rak'aat padhtey, unki qirat , rukoo aur sujood mein barabari hoti aur darmiyan mein koi tashahud ke liye na baithtey siwaye aathwin ke . aap us aathwin rakaat mein baithtey magar salam na phertey , balke khadey ho kar eik rakat witr padhtey . phir salam kehtey, eik salam , us mein aap ki aawaz bahut oonchi hoti yahan tak ke hamein jagaa detey. phir mazkura riwayat ke ham-maani bayan kiya."
1348,"Bahaz ne Zarara bin Ufee se riwayat kiya wo kehtey hain ke ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ke mutalliq sawal kiya gaya to unhoney kaha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) logon ko Isha ki Namaz padha kar ghar tashrif latey aur chaar rakaten padhtey phir apney bistar par aa jatey. ... aur hadees tafsil ke sath bayan ki . ... magar is mein ye zikr nahin kiya ke aap ( tahajjud ki rak'aat mein) qirat , rukoo aur sujood barabar rakhtey aur na salam hi ke baarey mein ye kaha ke aap us se hamen jagaa detey."
1349,"Bahaz bin Hakeem , Zarara bin Ufee sey, wo Saad bin Hisham se wo Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se yehi hadees riwayat kartey hain magar ye hadees unki riwayat ke barabar nahin hai. ( riwayaat Yazid bin Harun , ibne-Abi Adi aur Marwan bin Muaawiya)."
1350,"Abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko tehra rak'aat padhtey , no rakaten witr hotin . ... ya jaisey ke kaha . ... aur aap do rakaten padhtey baithey huey . aur Azan aur iqaamat ke darmiyan Fajr ki sunnaten padhtey."
1351,"Alqama bin Waqas Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( pahley ( no rakaat witr padha kartey they, phir saat rakaat padhney lagey . aap witron ke baad baith kar do rakaat padha kartey they, aap un mein qirat bhi kiya kartey they. jab aap rukoo karna chahtey to khadey ho jatey aur rukoo kartey phir sajda kartey. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Khalid bin Abdullah Waasti ne ye dono hadeesen (yani hadees Abi Salma aur Alqama ( Muhammad bin Amr se usi ke misl (jaisi) riwayat ki hai. un mein hai ke Alqama bin Waqas ne kaha : aey Ammaan jaan ! aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) do rakaten kaisey padha kartey they? to unhoney usi ke ham-maani bayan kiya."
1352,"Saad bin Hisham bayan kartey hain ke main Madiney aaya aur Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se mulaqat ki . maine arz kiya ke mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz ke mutalliq irshad farmaen . unhoney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) logon ko Isha ki Namaz padhatey , phir apney bistar par aa kar so jatey , phir raat ke darmiyani hisse mein uthtey , zarooriyaat se farigh hotey aur pani lekar wuzu kartey , phir apney musalley par aa jatey aur aath rakaten padhtey . mujhey mehsoos hota ke unki qirat , rukoo aur sujood barabar hotey , phir eik rakat witr padhtey , phir baith kar do rakaten padhtey , phir apna pehlu rakhtey , phir kabhi-kabhi Bilal aa jatey aur aap ko Namaz ki khabar detey , phir aap thoda sa so jatey , mujhey shak hota ke aap soey bhi hain ya nahin yahan tak ke wo aap ko Namaz ki khabar detey. aap ki Namaz aisey hi rahi yahan tak ke aap badi umr ke ho gaey aur kuchh bhari bhi. aur) Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne (aap ke kuchh farba ho janey ka zikr kiya. aur hadees bayan ki."
1353,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke wo ( eik baar ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan soey they. unhoney dekha ke aap jaagey , miswak ki aur wuzu kiya. us dauran mein aap ( إن في خلقِ السمواتِ والأرضِ ) se lekar aakhir surat tak tilawat farma rahey they. phir aap Namaz padhney ke liye khadey huey. aapney do rakaten padhein , unka qiyam , rukoo aur sujood bahut lamba kiya. phir aap paltey aur so gaey, yahan tak ke kharratey leney lagey. aapney is tarah teen baar kiya. chhe rakatein padhin. har baar aap uth kar miswak kartey , wuzu kartey aur mazkura aayaat ki tilawat kartey. phir aapney witr padhey. Usman ka bayan hai ke aapney teen rakaten padhin. phir muazzan aa gaya to aap Namaz ke liye tashrif ley gaey. Muhammad bin Isaa ne bayan kiya ke phir aapney witr padhey , phir Bilal aa gaey, unhoney aap ko Namaz ka waqt ho janey ki ittilaa di jabke Fajr tulu hui. phir aapney Fajr ki sunnaten padhein , phir aap Namaz ke liye tashrif ley gaey . uskey baad dono raawiyon ( ibne Isaa aur Usman (ka muttafiqa bayan hai ke Namaz ke liye jatey huey aap padh rahey they ( اللَّهُمَّ ! اجْعَلْ فِي قَلْبِي نُورًا , وَاجْعَلْ فِي لِسَانِي نُورًا , وَاجْعَلْ فِي سَمْعِي نُورًا , وَاجْعَلْ فِي بَصَرِي نُورًا , وَاجْعَلْ خَلْفِي نُورًا , وَأَمَامِي نُورًا , وَاجْعَلْ مِنْ فَوْقِي نُورًا , وَمِنْ تَحْتِي نُورًا , اللَّهُمَّ ! وَأَعْظِمْ لِي نُورًا ) ''aey Allah ! merey dil mein Noor bhar dey , meri zaban mein Noor kar dey , merey kanon mein Noor kar dey , meri aakhon mein Noor kar dey , merey peechhey Noor kar dey , merey aagey Noor kar dey , merey ooper Noor kar dey , merey nichey Noor kar dey. aey Allah ! merey liye Noor ko bahut azeem kar dey.''"
1354,"Khalid ne Husain se uskey jaisi hadees bayan ki aur kaha : (وأعظم لي نورا) yani ( اللهم (ke baghair . Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain : Abu-Khalid Dalani ne Habib se sabiqa riwayat mein aur is riwayat mein bhi aisey hi kaha hai. aur Salma bin Kuhail ne ba-waasta Abu-Rushdain , Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat ki hai."
1355,"Hazrat fazal bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke maine eik raat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ghar mein guzari taake dekhun ke aap Namaz kaisey padhtey hain. chunanche aap uthey , wuzu kiya aur do rakaten padhin. aap ka qiyam aap ke rukoo ki manind tha, aur aap ka rukoo aap ke sajdey ke jaisa. phir aap so gaey, phir jaagey , wuzu kiya, miswak ki, phir Sura Aale-Imran ki aakhiri paanch aayaten tilawat kin : ( { إِنَّ فِي khalaq السَّمَوَاتِ وَالْأَرْضِ وَاخْتِلَافِ اللَّيْلِ وَالنَّهَارِ . ... الخ } ) aap usi andaz mein kartey rahey yahan tak ke das rakaten padhein , phir khadey huey aur eik rakat padhi aur us se apni Namaz ko witr banaya. aur isi beech mein muazzan ne Azan kahi , to uskey khamosh honey ke baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne halki si do rakaten padhein phir baithe rahey yahan tak ke subah ki Namaz padhi . Imam Abu-Dawud kehtey hain ke main ibne Bashaar ki hadees ka baaz hissey sun nahin saka ( jis tarah ke main chahta tha)."
1356,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke maine apni khaala Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan raat guzari , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif laye jabkey raat ho chuki thi. aapney puchha : ''kya ladkey ne Namaz padh li hai? '' unhoney kaha : haan. chunanche aap bhi let gaey yahan tak ke jab raat ka kuchh hissey guzar gaya jo Allah ne chaha to aap uthey aur wuzu kiya. phir aapney saat ya paanch rak'aat padhein aur unhen witr banaya. aur un rak'aat mein aapney ( darmiyan mein) koi tashahud nahin kiya."
1357,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke maine apni khaala Hazrat Memuna binte Haris (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan raat guzari. chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Isha ki Namaz padhi , phir ghar mein tashrif laye aur chaar rakatein padhein , phir so rahey, phir jaagey aur Namaz padhney lagey . main bhi utha aur aap ki baain janib khada hua , to aapney mujh ko apni daain janib pher liya . phir aapney paanch rakaten padhin. phir so gaey, yahan tak ke maine aap ke kharratey suney . phir aap uthey aur do rakaten padhein , phir namaze-Fajr ke liye tashrif ley gaey."
1358,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne us qissey mein bayan kya ke aap uthey aur do do rakaten karkey Namaz padhi , yahan tak ke aath rakaten padhein , phir paanch rakatin witr padhey aur unke darmiyan mein tashahud ke liye nahin baithey."
1359,"Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Fajr ki sunnaton samet tera rakaten padha kartey they. chhe rakaten do do karkey , phir paanch witr aur un mein sirf aakhir hi mein baithtey they."
1360,Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat mein Fajr ki sunnaton samet tehra rak'aat padha kartey they.
1361,"Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Isha ki Namaz padhi , phir khadey ho kar aath rakaten padhein . aur dono azaanon ( Fajr ki Azan aur iqaamat (ke darmiyan do rakaten padhein aur aap unhen tarak na kiya kartey they. Jaafar bin Musafir ki riwayat hai ke do azaanon ke beech do rakaten baith kar padhtey . ye izafa ( baith kar) Jaafar bin Musafir ka hai."
1362,"Abdullah bin Ubai Qais kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kitni rak'aat witr padha kartey they? unhoney kaha : aap ( kabhi ( chaar aur teen , ( kabhi ( chhe aur teen ( kabhi ( aath aur teen aur) kabhi ( das aur teen rak'aat padha kartey they. aap ke witr saat se kam aur tehra rakaat se ziyada na hotey they. Imam Abu-Dawud ne kaha : Ahmed bin Saleh ne mazeed riwayat kiya ke aap Fajr se pehley do rakaten ''witr'' na kartey they. maine puchha ke witr kerney ka kya maani ? Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : ke aap ye rakaten chhoda na kartey they. aur Ahmed ne chhe aur teen rak'aat ka zikr nahin kiya."
1363,"Aswad bin Yazid se riwayat hai ke wo Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaye aur un se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki raat ki Namaz ke mutalliq daryaft kiya, to unhoney kaha : aap raat mein tehra rak'aat padha kartey they. phir giyara rak'aat padhney lagey aur do rakaten chhod di. phir jab aap ki wafat hui hai to aap raat ko no rak'aat padhtey they. aur aap ki aakhiri Namaz witr hua karti thi."
1364,"Kuraib maula ibne-Abbas kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko kaisey Namaz padhtey they? unhoney kaha : maine eik raat aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan guzari jabkey aap Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke ghar mein they. aap so gaey, jab tihai raat guzar gaee ya aadhi , to aap uthey , mishkeezey ki taraf gaey, us mein pani tha, aapney wuzu kiya, tab maine bhi aap ke sath wuzu kiya. phir aap khadey ho gaey, main bhi aap ke baeyn pehlu mein khada ho gaya , to aapney mujhey daain taraf kar liya . phir aapney apna haath merey sar par rakha goya aap merey kaan ko chhu rahey hon, mujhey jagaa rahey hon, to aapney do rakatein padhein halki halki , main samajhta hun ke aapney her rakaat mein sura Fatiha padhi , phir salam phera . yahan tak ke giyara rakaten padhein witr samet , phir so gaey, yahan tak ke aap ke paas Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) aaye aur kaha : Namaz , aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap khadey huey, do rakaten padhin. phir logon ko Namaz padhaai."
1365,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke maine apni khaala Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan raat guzari . isliye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) raat ko uthey aur Namaz padhney lagey. aapney tehra rak'aat padhein , un mein Fajr ki sunnaten bhi shamil thin . maine har rakaat mein aap ke qiyam ka andaza lagaya ke sura muzammil ke barabar tha. Nooh ne apni riwayat mein Fajr ki sunnaton ka zikr nahin kiya."
1366,"Hazrat Zaid bin Khalid Juhni (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine kaha : aaj raat mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki Namaz dekhun ga . chunanche maine aap ke darwazey ya khemey ki chaukhat ko apna takiya bana liya , isliye aapney do rakaten padhein halki halki , phir do rakaten padhein lambi lambi , phir do rakaten padhein jo un se qadrey kam lambi thin , phir do rakaten padhein jo un se kam thin , phir do rakaten padhein jo un se kam thin , phir do rakaten padhein jo un se kam thin , phir (eik) witr padha. ye (mukammal) tehra rak'aat huin."
1367,"Kuraib maula ibne-Abbas ka bayan hai ke Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne unko bataya ke maine Ummul-momenin Hazrat Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan raat guzari aur wo unki khaala thin . farmatey hain : main takiye ke arz mein let gaya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ki ehliya uskey lambaee mein let gaey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) so gaey, yahan tak ke jab aadhi raat hui ya us se kuchh pehley ka waqt hoga ya baad ka to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jaag gaey . aap uth kar baith gaey aur apney haath se apna chehra mala , goya neend door kartey hon. phir aapney Sura Aale-Imran ki aakhiri das aayaten padhin, phir aap eik mishkeezey ki taraf gaey jo latak raha tha, us se aapney wuzu kiya aur achchha wuzu kiya, phir Namaz padhney khadey ho gaey . Hazrat Abdullah farmatey hain : phir main bhi uth khada hua aur jaisey aapney kiya tha maine bhi kiya aur aap ke) baeyn ( pehlu mein ja khada hua . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna daayan haath merey sar par rakha , mera kaan pakda aur usey kuchh maroda . aapney do rakaten padhein , phir do rakaten , phir do rakaten , phir do rakaten , phir do rakaten , phir do rakaten . Qaanabi ne kaha ke chhe baar ( do do rakaten padhin.) phir ( eik ( witr padha . uskey baad let gaey, yahan tak ke aap ke paas muazzan aaya to aapney uth kar halki si do rakaten padhein , phir tashrif ley gaey aur Fajr ki Namaz padhi."
1368,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''amal usi qadr ikhtiyar karo jiski tum mein taqat ho kyonkey Shan wala Allah (tumhen sawab denaey sey) nahin uktaataa , yahan tak ke tum hi (amal sey) uktaa jao. bila-shuba Shan Wale Allah ko wohi amal mehboob hai jo hamesha ho agar-che thoda hi ho.'' aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab koi amal ikhtiyar kartey to us par hameshgi kartey they."
1369,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Usman bin Maz'oon (Raziallahu anhu) ko apney paas bulwaya . wo aap ke paas aaye to aapney farmaya : ''aey Usman ! kya tum ne meri sunnat ( taur tareeqey ( se aeraz kar liya hai? '' unhoney kaha : nahin, qasam Allah ki ! aey Allah ke Rasool ! balke main to aap ki sunnat hi ka mutalaashi hun. aapney farmaya : ''phir main to sota bhi hun aur Namaz bhi padhta hun. rozey rakhta bhi hun aur chhodta bhi hun. aurton se nikah bhi kiya hai. isliye Allah se daro , aey Usman ! yaqinan tumharey ghar walon ka bhi tum par haq hai. tumharey mehman ka bhi tum par haq hai. tumhari jaan ka bhi tum par haq hai. lihaza rozey rakho aur chhod bhi diya karo . Namaz padha karo aur soyaa bhi karo.''"
1370,"Janab Alqama bayan kartey hain, maine Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke aamaal ka kya andaz tha, kya aapney koi din khas kar rakhey they? unhoney kaha : nahin, aap ke her amal mein hameshgi hoti thi aur tum mein wo istataat kahan jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko hasil thi."
